-- Switchblade --

Switchblade glances over Pheonix, staring at her intensely. His gaze 
rakes over her slowly, then he looks away, to the front of the 
control room.

"Computer, display the nearest path from control room to the CR 
chambers." The computer obliges him, and a small map appears.

He shrugs, the speaks again, "Follow the path; don't get lost." Two 
dots light up on the map, a green glowing dot for Switchblade, and a 
dull reddish dot for Pheonix.
